---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro'
---

<Layout category="company">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">회사개요</h1>

    <div class="max-w-6xl">
      <div
        class="flex justify-center items-center
        border border-gray-300
        rounded-lg p-8"
      >
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="" />
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <ul
          class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 border-t-2 border-[#d84144]"
        >
          <li class="flex items-center py-5 border-b border-gray-300">
            <div
              class="min-w-[120px] text-lg font-semibold text-[#242424] tracking-tight relative pl-8"
            >
              대표이사
            </div>
            <div class="leading-relaxed">양 영 수</div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center py-5 border-b border-gray-300">
            <div
              class="min-w-[120px] text-lg font-semibold text-[#242424] tracking-tight relative pl-8"
            >
              설립일
            </div>
            <div class="leading-relaxed">2019년 5월</div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center py-5 border-b border-gray-300">
            <div
              class="min-w-[120px] text-lg font-semibold text-[#242424] tracking-tight relative pl-8"
            >
              업종
            </div>
            <div class="leading-relaxed">기업컨설팅</div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center py-5 border-b border-gray-300">
            <div
              class="min-w-[120px] text-lg font-semibold text-[#242424] tracking-tight relative pl-8"
            >
              주요업무
            </div>
            <div class="leading-relaxed">
              주주총회 대행 / 의결권 Proxy업무 / M&amp;A / 자금조달 제휴사를
              통한 세무·회계·법무 등 Total Service
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center py-5 border-b border-gray-300">
            <div
              class="min-w-[120px] text-lg font-semibold text-[#242424] tracking-tight relative pl-8"
            >
              주소
            </div>
            <div class="leading-relaxed">서울시 강남구 테헤란로6길 30. 4층</div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center py-5 border-b border-gray-300">
            <div
              class="min-w-[120px] text-lg font-semibold text-[#242424] tracking-tight relative pl-8"
            >
              연락처
            </div>
            <div class="leading-relaxed">02-556-2260 (Fax: 02-556-2260 )</div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
